sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as KServe Controller<br/>Manager
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/OCI/HF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>(init container)
    participant Gateway as OpenShift Gateway<br/>(openshift-ai-inference)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (RawDeployment Mode)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate request<br/>mTLS (webhook CA)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: new InferenceService
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute or VirtualService<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over StorageInit,Storage: Pod startup - model download
    StorageInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: Storage credentials (storage-config secret)
    Storage-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 2: Inference Request (Gateway API Mode)

    participant Client as External Client

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>HTTP/80 (cluster-internal)
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Prediction response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 3: LLMInferenceService with Scheduler

    participant Scheduler as llm-d Scheduler<br/>(InferencePool endpoint-picker)
    participant LLMPod as LLM Serving Pod<br/>(vLLM) 8080/TCP

    Client->>Gateway: POST inference request<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>Scheduler: Route via InferencePool<br/>HTTP/80 plaintext
    Scheduler->>LLMPod: Intelligent request routing<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
    LLMPod-->>Scheduler: LLM response
    Scheduler-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS
